        <main>
            <div class="about-us">
                <h1>About Us</h1>
                <img src="img/fancy hotel exterior.jpg" alt="Flora Hotels' exterior" height="19%" width="88%"/>
                <p>Flora Hotels self-imposed mission is to create a welcoming environment for people to stay in all around the world. Our aim isn't just to offer a temporary place to stay for our customers travelling plans but we want them to consider us like their second home! Through our top-notch services, staff and facilities we aim to exceed customers' satisfactions and standards </p>
            </div>
            <div class="food" id="continue-food">
                <h2 style="margin-bottom: 60px; text-align:center;">Food and Drinks</h2>
                <div class="container-food_drinks">
                    <img src="img/hotel resturant.jpg" alt="hotel resturant" style="height:100%;width:40%;">
                    <p>Our in-doors hotel dining restaurants are equipped with international chefs to reproduce any cuisine and provide our customers with their typical home dishes! We want our customers to be reminded f home while consuming their main 3 meals of the day.</p>
                </div>
                <br>
                <p>Our food is made with the most natural and nutritional ingredients as we care about our customer health. Every ingredient is from the country the hotel is residing in while following their necessary rules and regulations. We also can take into consideration any diet plans or allergies, provided that they were mentioned on the day of Check In. Drinks are included for every meal and can be picked up in the bar department.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="container-rooms" id="continue-room">
                <h2>Our Rooms</h2>
                <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
