                <p style="text-align:center;">Our rooms are furnished with the best quality of imports from Turkey and Italy. Each room has got a lush bathroom and a spacious balcony. Discounts and Promotions for the rooms can be found in our deals page!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="container-location" id="continue-location">
                <h2 style="text-align:center;">Our Locations</h2>
                <h3>List of Locations:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>United Kingdon</li>
                    <li>Italy</li>
                    <li>Germany</li>
                    <li>Spain</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="button-parent">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" style="width:48%">Click to scroll</button>
                </div>
                <p>Flora Hotels takes pride in possessing branches in some of the most famous locations worldwide. Our properties are always close to key attractions of the country to better your travel experience.</p>
